{"tid":1317032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（要keep住士氣！士氣！士氣！）不想打！不怕打！不得不打！","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T18:21:17.000Z","uid":264683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8791a46c6e37a65fc1a77fed6d279acdbda4aa","tid":1317032,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"今日玩沙田online嘅手足<br />\n我地最期待嘅畫面終於出現！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好可惜今日被圍毆嘅唔係柒婆</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沙田一役將會係今後抗爭模式轉捩點！</span><br />\n<br />\n柒婆，<br />\n係你教我地和平遊行係冇用！<br />\n多得你派咁多黑警比我地呢一個月不斷刷經驗值<br />\n我地一眾隊友終於成功覺醒<br />\n結構性轉型成功<br />\n<br />\n我話比你條柒婆知<br />\n我地唔止<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化！不篤灰！不割蓆！</span><br />\n我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不想打！不怕打！不得不打！</span></span><br />\n今後你唔洗諗住好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHyFMEY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHyFMEY.png&h=bf5dd521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要keep住個勢！<br />\n打倒HK Police state！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSor1999太激動振奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家之後嘅副本再見</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a99f171f0c2946961745797c06b89ad2ea9d5e7","tid":1317032,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"【帶領輿論】由強調自己手無寸鐵，升級至以武制暴嘅正當性！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316840</a><br />\n<br />\n唔使再話自己冇打過警察、冇警察受傷，<br />\n而係要講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日警察比示威者反擊，係合理而正當嘅反抗，係佢哋自己造成！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm